name: 𝔰𝔬𝔪𝔢𝔴𝔥𝔢𝔯𝔢
description:
I decided to create something different, I found the result interesting... this is a photo taken on my first trip
by bicycle, and for hours we cycled along the road, until we found the beginning of a forest that followed a road through the trees
funny how this pixelated image brings me good memories, I don't have the original photo... just a pixelated memory.
